name: Art Train.
description: All Aboard the ART TRAIN! We all know the fun, so let's get it done! Captured in San Francisco; the local well-known trolleys share the rails with cars brought from cities throughout the US, sort of in a way to keep a "living" display of the heritage of the Metro Rail Systems; and of course, tourism.
